hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I like watching TV viagra precio farmacias del ahorro Same thing happened to Pat and Kevin Williams…ultimately the NFL won and they both served their four game suspensions. They took Starcaps and the banned diuretic was not listed as an ingredient. They NEVER took steriods and were tested specifically for steriods after the diuretic was detected. Evidently, the particular chemical will mask the use of steroids so the NFL put the substance on the banned list. Didn’t matter, banned is banned according to the NFL. I personally think the Williams’ should have been able to sue Starcaps for the lost four game checks but they didn’t.
